✅ Day 5 – Story & Insights

Story 

A valuable opportunity can make a better future for you, if you can see it.
You should use it well, but it is not easy.
It needs courage and a brave heart.
You may face many obstacles, but you must prepare yourself if you want the best result.
And you should take care of yourself, because you are the most important person in your life.
So, you can make the impossible possible.


---

Words: Courage • Opportunity • Valuable • Prepare • Opportunity

---

What I Learned

✔️ Opportunity: use singular form and refer to it with it → “A valuable opportunity… if you can see it.”

✔️ Brave (adj): we need an adjective to describe a heart or person → brave heart.

✔️ Result: common verbs used with result are want or get.

 ✔️Common expressions:

▫️Take care of someone

▫️You can make the impossible possible
